# Design System — Bunyan (Vercel-Inspired)

**Source of truth**: `DESIGN.md` (project root)

Always read `DESIGN.md` before generating any frontend UI code.

## Core Principles

- Geist Sans with aggressive negative letter-spacing at display sizes
- Shadow-as-border: `box-shadow: 0px 0px 0px 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.08)` replaces CSS borders
- Achromatic palette: grays from `#171717` to `#ffffff`
- Three weights only: 400 (body), 500 (UI), 600 (headings)
- Ligatures (`"liga"`) enabled on all Geist text

## Color Palette

### Primary

- Vercel Black: `#171717` (text, headings — NOT pure black)
- Pure White: `#ffffff` (backgrounds, card surfaces)

### Workflow Accents (functional only)

- Ship Red: `#ff5b4f`
- Preview Pink: `#de1d8d`
- Develop Blue: `#0a72ef`

### Interactive

- Link Blue: `#0072f5`
- Focus Blue: `hsla(212, 100%, 48%, 1)`

### Neutral Scale

- Gray 900: `#171717` | Gray 600: `#4d4d4d` | Gray 500: `#666666`
- Gray 400: `#808080` | Gray 100: `#ebebeb` | Gray 50: `#fafafa`

## Typography Hierarchy

| Role            | Size | Weight  | Letter Spacing    |
| --------------- | ---- | ------- | ----------------- |
| Display Hero    | 48px | 600     | -2.4px to -2.88px |
| Section Heading | 40px | 600     | -2.4px            |
| Sub-heading     | 32px | 600     | -1.28px           |
| Card Title      | 24px | 600     | -0.96px           |
| Body Large      | 20px | 400     | normal            |
| Body            | 16px | 400     | normal            |
| Button          | 14px | 500     | normal            |
| Caption         | 12px | 400-500 | normal            |

## Shadow System

| Level            | Shadow                                                                | Use                |
| ---------------- | --------------------------------------------------------------------- | ------------------ |
| Ring (L1)        | `rgba(0,0,0,0.08) 0px 0px 0px 1px`                                    | Border replacement |
| Light Ring (L1b) | `rgb(235,235,235) 0px 0px 0px 1px`                                    | Tabs, images       |
| Subtle Card (L2) | Ring + `rgba(0,0,0,0.04) 0px 2px 2px`                                 | Standard cards     |
| Full Card (L3)   | Ring + Subtle + `rgba(0,0,0,0.04) 0px 8px 8px -8px` + `#fafafa` inner | Featured cards     |

## Component Patterns

### Buttons

- Primary: `#171717` bg, `#ffffff` text, 6px radius, 8px 16px padding
- Secondary: `#ffffff` bg, shadow-border, 6px radius
- Pill Badge: `#ebf5ff` bg, `#0068d6` text, 9999px radius

### Cards

- White bg, NO CSS border, shadow stack, 8px radius
- Inner `#fafafa` ring creates subtle glow

### Border Radius Scale

- 2px (inline code) → 6px (buttons) → 8px (cards) → 12px (images) → 9999px (pills)

## Do's and Don'ts

- DO use shadow-as-border instead of CSS `border`
- DO use `#171717` not `#000000` for primary text
- DO scale letter-spacing with font size
- DON'T use weight 700 on body text
- DON'T use warm colors in UI chrome
- DON'T skip the inner `#fafafa` ring in card shadows
